  "prompt": "Who are the top interior designers in pune?",
  "response": "Pune, a vibrant city in Maharashtra, is home to several talented interior designers and firms known for their creativity and expertise. Here are some of the top interior designers in Pune as of recent years:\n\n### 1. **Sekhon Arora Interiors**\n   - Renowned for their modern and elegant designs, Sekhon Arora Interiors specializes in both residential and commercial projects. Their work reflects a perfect blend of functionality and aesthetics.\n\n### 2. **Bonito & Designs**\n   - A well-known interior design firm in Pune, Bonito Designs offers end-to-end interior solutions with a focus on personalized and modular designs. They are known for their innovative and cost-effective designs.\n\n### 3. **Design Thoughts Associates (DTA)**\n   - Led by Ar. Biki Kale, DTA is celebrated for its contemporary and timeless designs. They focus on creating spaces that are both functional and visually appealing.\n\n### 4. **Ashwin Architects**\n   - Known for their creative and sustainable designs, Ashwin Architects specialize in residential, commercial, and hospitality projects. Their designs often emphasize natural elements and eco-friendliness.\n\n### 5. **Design Konstruct**\n   - A versatile interior design firm, Design Konstruct is known for transforming spaces into luxurious and functional environments. Their portfolio includes residential, retail, and office interiors.\n\n### 6. **Elegancia Interior Designers**\n   - Elegancia is recognized for its classic and elegant designs. They offer a wide range of services, including interior decoration, furniture design, and space planning.\n\n### 7. **Urban Living Interiors**\n   - Known for their modern and minimalist designs, Urban Living Interiors creates spaces that are clutter-free and stylish. They specialize in residential and commercial projects.\n\n### 8. **Cubic Spaces**\n   - Cubic Spaces is known for its innovative and contemporary designs. They focus on creating spaces that reflect the personality and preferences of their clients.\n\n### 9. **Antrass Interiors**\n   - Antrass Interiors is known for its unique and creative designs. They specialize in both residential and commercial projects, offering bespoke interior solutions.\n\n### 10. **The Acer Interiors**\n   - The Acer Interiors is known for its sophisticated and stylish designs. They offer a range of services, from interior design to execution, ensuring a seamless experience for their clients.\n\n### 11. **De Panache**\n   - De Panache is known for its luxurious and high-end designs. They specialize in creating opulent interiors for residences, offices, and hospitality spaces.\n\n### 12. **I-Rise Interiors**\n   - I-Rise Interiors is known for their contemporary and functional designs. They focus on creating spaces that are both beautiful and practical.\n\nThese designers and firms are highly regarded in Pune for their expertise, creativity, and ability to deliver exceptional results. When choosing an interior designer, it's essential to review their portfolio, understand their design philosophy, and ensure they align with your vision and requirements.",
